<br>
I am thinking about buying a Lodi shield.  Given the absence of hit points or stamina, is this an item for the long term?  I hesitate to buy it if there are newer/better items that might be easier to obtain.<br>
<br>
For reference, I am not currently in a guild that is raiding areas where I might find really nice no-drop gear, so I am looking at either this shield or another droppable item I can hunt/buy.<br>
<br>
Thanks in advance,<br>
<br>
